Source-Makefile: feeds/packages/libs/libnfc/Makefile
Package: libnfc
Version: 1.3.4-1
Depends: +libpcsclite +libusb +pcscd +ccid
Provides: 
Build-Depends: libtool libintl libiconv
Section: libs
Category: Libraries
Title: Near Field Communication (NFC) library
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libnfc-1.3.4.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:   libnfc is a free software library used to communicate with NFC 
  capable devices or tags. It support the four main NFC modulations:
  * ISO14443-A (NXP MIFARE),
  * ISO14443-B,
  * JIS X 6319-4 (Sony Felica) and
  * Jewel Topaz (Innovision Research & Development).
  Supported NFC hardware devices are theorically all readers based 
  on the NXP PN53x NFC Controller.
http://www.libnfc.org
@@

Package: libnfc-examples
Version: 1.3.4-1
Depends: +libnfc
Provides: 
Build-Depends: libtool libintl libiconv
Section: utils
Category: Utilities
Title: Near Field Communication (NFC) library
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libnfc-1.3.4.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:   libnfc is provided with some examples like:
   * tag listing
   * relaying NFC
   * simple UID emulation
http://www.libnfc.org
